  Unit dtpBitmapShape

  TdtpBitmapShape is a TdtpEffectShape descendant that can be used to show
  bitmap (raster) images. Raster formats that are supported can be found
  in the unit dtpRasterFormats. Additional formats can be added.

  Project: DTP-Engine

